                        <persName xml:lang="per" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656473.0x000001 viaf_211269318">افضل الدّين محمّد كاشى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <note>
                        <p>Item b. </p>
                        <p>Untitled Sufi treatise on the legitimacy of the congregation or jamāʿat evidently by <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656473.0x000001 viaf_211269318" role="aut">Afz̤al al-Dīn Muḥammad Kāshī </persName>(d. 707/1307-8), who is mentioned at the beginning simply as Afz̤al. 
                        </p>
                        <p>The brief work mentions the opinions of a certain <persName key="viaf_19930855" role="oth">Mīr Sayyid Sharīf</persName>. 
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
                     </note>
