                     <locus from="278v" to="279r">ff. 278v-279r</locus>
                     <author/>
                     <note>
                        <p>Item ll. </p>
                        <p>Untitled Arabic treatise discussing Shīʿī aḥādīs̲ or traditions concerning to the <orgName>Ahl al-Bayt</orgName> or family of the <persName key="viaf_97245226" role="subject">Prophet Muḥammad</persName> related by <persName key="person_f7175" role="ant">Ibn ʿAbbās</persName> in the works of [<persName key="viaf_73824880" role="ant">Abū ʿAbd Allāh Muḥammad ibn Yazīd al-Qazvīnī</persName>] <persName key="viaf_73824880" role="ant">Ibn Mājah</persName> (d. 273/887).  
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="ara">Arabic</textLang>
